{"tid":1158863,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"李慧琼：下星期才討論法案委員會問題","createTime":"2019-05-17T09:25:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-17T10:16:45.000Z","uid":144372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6930b3a652cee25e2e2938ac0e588dfc2a036fcd","tid":1158863,"uid":144372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T09:25:41.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】立法會內務委員會討論，由石禮謙向內會主席尋求主持逃犯條例法案委員會的新指示。<br />\n<br />\n星期二石禮謙去信內會主席李慧琼，提出自己無法再主持逃犯條例草案委員會，向內會尋求新指示。李慧琼表示明白到事件具爭議，無意要求議員在今次會議作出決定，會先容許議員討論委員會運作的未來路向，若有議員想提出方案，請於下星期二或以前提出，之後會安排多一次會議討論。<br />\n<br />\n李慧琼又表示，已將部分議員就修例的關注轉達予政務司司長張建宗，對方表示政府若有意見提出會通知立法會秘書處，但秘書處至今未有答覆。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.mobi.yahoo.com/news/李慧琼-內會暫無意下達新指示-074030414.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.mobi.yahoo.com%2Fnews%2F%E6%9D%8E%E6%85%A7%E7%90%BC-%E5%85%A7%E6%9C%83%E6%9A%AB%E7%84%A1%E6%84%8F%E4%B8%8B%E9%81%94%E6%96%B0%E6%8C%87%E7%A4%BA-074030414.html&d=2bx9SR3QHfMC8bM4fPAEX5riIWEbfV0cuvPRs67P9cA%3D&h=a3a8be7e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.mobi.yahoo.com/news/李慧琼-內會暫無意下達新指示-074030414.html</a>"},{"pid":"f2bd6682f47aa9d5aa4f481e2762e32267ee2e86","tid":1158863,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T09:27:19.000Z","msg":"琼子都射波？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n定係鋪排做啲咩⋯⋯⋯"},{"pid":"7701c830961bbb8998f270256fb9b62838ae7084","tid":1158863,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f2bd6682f47aa9d5aa4f481e2762e32267ee2e86","tid":1158863,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T09:27:19.000Z","msg":"琼子都射波？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n定係鋪排做啲咩⋯⋯⋯"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"201